[SN]TITLE[SN]
Barcelona: Sergio Busquets signs five-year deal with £152m clause

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Sergio Busquets has agreed a new five-year deal at Barcelona that includes a buyout clause of £152m.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 27-year-old midfielder's contract could also be extended to 2023, depending on how many games he plays.
Spain lynchpin Busquets has made 384 appearances for the La Liga champions, scoring 12 goals.
He has won 23 major honours with Barcelona, including six top-flight titles and the Champions League in 2009, 2011 and 2015.
